ntial futures of the discipline in a global context, offering insight into some of the most pressing issues of our time.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Economy.2bisacsh1 aAlbo, Greg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aArmstrong, Hugh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aArmstrong, Pat, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlack, Simon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChoiniere, Jacqueline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aClement, Wallace, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDaly, Tamara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFanelli, Carlo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFanelli, Carlo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGraefe, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaley, Tobin LeBlanc, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHall, Rebecca Jane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLyubchenko, Olena, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLyubchenko, Olena, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMcBride, Stephen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMills, Suzanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMirrlees, Tanner, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRoss, Stephanie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharma, Nandita, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSmith, Adrian A., econtributor.4ctb4